@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram for Ott Based System Mini Reel

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User starts creating account
CreateAccount : do / Fill details and submit
CreateAccount : exit / Account created successfully

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / User watches videos after account creation
WatchVideos : exit / Watching video completed

state "Upload Video" as UploadVideo
UploadVideo : entry / User uploads a video
UploadVideo : do / Fill details and submit
UploadVideo : exit / Video uploaded successfully

state "Save to Likes List" as SaveToLikesList
SaveToLikesList : entry / User saves video in likes list during viewing
SaveToLikesList : exit / Video saved in likes list

state "View Likes List" as ViewLikesList
ViewLikesList : entry / User views saved videos from likes list
ViewLikesList : exit / Viewing likes list completed

state "Enter Discussion Option" as EnterDiscussionOption
EnterDiscussionOption : entry / User enters discussion option
EnterDiscussionOption : do / Participate in discussion
EnterDiscussionOption : exit / Discussion entered

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos
WatchVideos --> UploadVideo
UploadVideo --> SaveToLikesList
SaveToLikesList --> ViewLikesList
ViewLikesList --> EnterDiscussionOption
EnterDiscussionOption --> [*]

@enduml
